# Third-Party Type Sourcing Policy

## Third-Party Imports
- Prefer library-native exported types first using type-only imports.
- If native types are missing, use `@types/<package>` when available.

## Custom Type Creation
- Create custom interfaces/types only as a last resort, after built-in, inferred, and third-party types are confirmed insufficient or unavailable.
